etween the perpetual future price and the underlying index. The rate is determined by the 8-hour TWAP of the premium, but payment occurs hourly, creating more frequent settlement cycles. As a rollup-based DEX, Aevo's funding calculations are processed off-chain and settled on-chain, allowing for more responsive rate adjustments compared to traditional AMM-based platforms."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
